marc21:datafield.marc21:subfield: Scrapbook contains press clippings and other printed ephemera. Includes reviews (mostly negative) of Kootz's book New Frontiers in American Painting; articles on the "Bombshell Group" of artists which arose in response to his statements about American Art in the New York Times; articles and promotional materials for a sale of paintings selected by Kootz held at Macy's; and reviews of Kootz's play Home is the Hunter as it was performed at the American Negro Theatre.
Archives of American Art, Smithsonian Institution
